# Activity 跳转动画衔接 + WMS 代码流程完整梳理

[知识来源: AOSP master 实测 - AppTransition / AppTransitionController / Transition / TransitionController / WindowOrganizerController / ActivityOptions / ActivityStarter / ActivityStartController / TaskFragment / DisplayContent 2026-07-18]
[知识来源: 4 引擎 Web 搜索并行 - serper/ddg/tavily/MiniMax 2026-07-18]
[置信度: 高]

## 0. 一句话答案

`startActivity` → `ActivityStarter.startActivityInner` → `ActivityRecord.setOptions(...)` → 切换 `mDisplayContent.mOpeningApps/mClosingApps` → `AppTransition.prepareAppTransition` 设置 `mNextAppTransition` 状态机为 **READY** → **`AppTransitionController.handleAppTransitionReady`** 在 `mSurfaceAnimationRunner` 解冻窗口后调 `applyAnimations` → `WindowContainer.applyAnimation` 走 `TransitionAnimation` 加载 `R.anim.activity_open_enter/exit` → `SurfaceAnimator` 应用到 `SurfaceControl`，SurfaceFlinger 跑动画；同时 **新版本 (Android 14+)** 在 `isShellTransitionsEnabled` 启用时绕过整套 AppTransition，改走 `TransitionController.createTransition` → `WindowOrganizerController.startTransition` → 交给 systemui `Shell Transitions` 由 launcher 提供 `IRemoteAnimationRunner` 在远端进程画动画。

## 1. 系统状态字段（实测）

### 1.1 DisplayContent（衔接点）

```java
// DisplayContent.java:1163/1166  构造里
mAppTransition = new AppTransition(mWmService.mContext, mWmService, this);
mAppTransitionController = new AppTransitionController(mWmService, this);
```

- `mAppTransition` —— 旧版 transition 状态机（每个 display 一个）
- `mAppTransitionController` —— 协调"窗口已就绪 → 加载动画 → 应用到 SF"
- `mTransitionController` —— **新版** Shell Transitions 入口（TransitionController.java）
- `mOpeningApps: ArraySet<ActivityRecord>` / `mClosingApps: ArraySet<ActivityRecord>` —— 参与本次 transition 的窗口集合

### 1.2 AppTransition（master 字段实测）

```java
// AppTransition.java:154
public class AppTransition implements Dump {

    private @TransitionFlags int mNextAppTransitionFlags = 0;            // L173
    private final ArrayList<Integer> mNextAppTransitionRequests = ...;   // L174
    private int mNextAppTransitionType = NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_NONE;        // L198  ★ 状态机核心
    private boolean mNextAppTransitionOverrideRequested;                // L199
    private String mNextAppTransitionPackage;                           // L201
    private boolean mNextAppTransitionScaleUp;                          // L203
    private IRemoteCallback mNextAppTransitionCallback;                 // L204
    private IRemoteCallback mNextAppTransitionFutureCallback;          // L205
    private int mNextAppTransitionEnter;                                // L207  ★ 启动 Activity enter 动画
    private int mNextAppTransitionExit;                                 // L208  ★ 当前 Activity exit 动画
    private @ColorInt int mNextAppTransitionBackgroundColor;            // L209
    private int mNextAppTransitionInPlace;                              // L210
    private boolean mNextAppTransitionIsSync;                           // L211
    private final SparseArray<AppTransitionAnimationSpec> mNextAppTransitionAnimationsSpecs ...;  // L214
    private IAppTransitionAnimationSpecsFuture mNextAppTransitionAnimationsSpecsFuture;  // L216
    private boolean mNextAppTransitionAnimationsSpecsPending;           // L217
    private int mAppTransitionState = APP_STATE_IDLE;                   // L226  ★ 4 态状态机
    private @TransitionOldType int mLastUsedAppTransition = TRANSIT_OLD_UNSET;  // L175
}
```

**状态机常量**（AppTransition.java:222-226）：
```java
private final static int APP_STATE_IDLE    = 0;   // 空闲，可开始新一轮
private final static int APP_STATE_READY   = 1;   // 已就绪（窗口全部 drawn），可走 transitionGoodToGo
private final static int APP_STATE_RUNNING = 2;   // 动画播放中
private final static int APP_STATE_TIMEOUT = 3;   // 等待窗口超时
```

**`mNextAppTransitionType` 枚举**（AppTransition.java:180-196）：
```java
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_NONE                    = 0
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_CUSTOM                  = 1   // ActivityOptions.makeCustomAnimation
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_SCALE_UP                = 2
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_THUMBNAIL_SCALE_UP      = 3
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_THUMBNAIL_SCALE_DOWN    = 4
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_THUMBNAIL_ASPECT_SCALE_UP   = 5
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_THUMBNAIL_ASPECT_SCALE_DOWN = 6
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_CUSTOM_IN_PLACE         = 7
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_CLIP_REVEAL             = 8
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_OPEN_CROSS_PROFILE_APPS = 9
NEXT_TRANSIT_TYPE_REMOTE                  = 10  // RemoteAnimation
```

## 2. 旧路径（AppTransition 状态机）— 实测

### 2.1 入口：`ActivityStarter.startActivityInner`

```java
// ActivityStarter.java:1863
int startActivityInner(final ActivityRecord r, ..., ActivityOptions options, ...) {
    setInitialState(r, options, inTask, inTaskFragment, startFlags, ...);  // L1868
    ...
    mTargetRootTask.moveToFront("startActivityInner");                     // L2091
}
```

`setInitialState` (ActivityStarter.java:2650) 把 `options` 赋给 `mOptions` (L2658) — 这是后续 `ActivityRecord.setOptions(...)` 的来源。

### 2.2 衔接：ActivityRecord.setOptions 准备 transition

`ActivityRecord.setOptions` 把 `mPendingOptions` 设置到 window token 容器上，由 WMS `WindowManagerService.addWindow` → `addWindowToken` → `WindowManagerService.relayoutWindow` 链路触发 `mDisplayContent.mAppTransitionController` 把 activity 放进 `mOpeningApps` 或 `mClosingApps` 集合。

### 2.3 触发：`AppTransition.prepareAppTransition`

```java
// AppTransition.java:1464
boolean prepareAppTransition(@TransitionType int transit, @TransitionFlags int flags) {
    if (mDisplayContent.mTransitionController.isShellTransitionsEnabled()) {
        return false;   // ★ 新版 Shell Transitions 接管时直接 return false
    }
    mNextAppTransitionRequests.add(transit);
    mNextAppTransitionFlags |= flags;
    updateBooster();
    removeAppTransitionTimeoutCallbacks();
    mHandler.postDelayed(mHandleAppTransitionTimeoutRunnable, APP_TRANSITION_TIMEOUT_MS);
    return prepare();
}
```

调用方典型路径：
- `WindowManagerService.addWindow` (启动 activity 时)
- `Task.moveTaskToFront` / `ActivityTaskManagerService.moveTaskToFront`
- `startActivityFromRecents` (ActivityStarter.java L2474 段 diff 命中)
- `WindowContainer.reparent` / 各种 transition 入口

### 2.4 衔接核心：`AppTransitionController.handleAppTransitionReady`

```java
// AppTransitionController.java:169  master 实测
void handleAppTransitionReady() {
    mTempTransitionReasons.clear();
    if (!transitionGoodToGo(mDisplayContent.mOpeningApps, mTempTransitionReasons)
            || !transitionGoodToGo(mDisplayContent.mChangingContainers, mTempTransitionReasons)
            || !transitionGoodToGoForTaskFragments()) {
        return;        // ★ 窗口还没就绪就不走
    }
    Trace.traceBegin(Trace.TRACE_TAG_WINDOW_MANAGER, "AppTransitionReady");
    ProtoLog.v(WM_DEBUG_APP_TRANSITIONS, "**** GOOD TO GO");

    mDisplayContent.forAllWindows(WindowState::cleanupAnimatingExitWindow, true);
    final AppTransition appTransition = mDisplayContent.mAppTransition;

    // 1) 清理 mAnimatingExit / 调整壁纸
    for (int i = 0; i < mDisplayContent.mOpeningApps.size(); ++i)
        mDisplayContent.mOpeningApps.valueAtUnchecked(i).clearAnimatingFlags();
    ...
    mWallpaperControllerLocked.adjustWallpaperWindowsForAppTransitionIfNeeded(...);

    // 2) 收集 opening/closing 集合
    ArraySet<ActivityRecord> tmpOpenApps = mDisplayContent.mOpeningApps;
    ArraySet<tmpCloseApps = mDisplayContent.mClosingApps;
    if (mAtmService.mBackNavigationController.isMonitoringFinishTransition()) {
        // 预测式返回动画过滤
        if (mAtmService.mBackNavigationController.removeIfContainsBackAnimationTargets(
                tmpOpenApps, tmpCloseApps)) {
            mAtmService.mBackNavigationController.clearBackAnimations(false);
        }
    }

    // 3) 决定 transit 类型
    @TransitionOldType final int transit = getTransitCompatType(
            mDisplayContent.mAppTransition, tmpOpenApps, tmpCloseApps,
            mDisplayContent.mChangingContainers,
            mWallpaperControllerLocked.getWallpaperTarget(), getOldWallpaper(),
            mDisplayContent.mSkipAppTransitionAnimation);

    // 4) 检查 RemoteAnimation / TaskFragment RemoteAnimation 覆盖
    if (!overrideWithTaskFragmentRemoteAnimation(transit, activityTypes)) {
        unfreezeEmbeddedChangingWindows();
        overrideWithRemoteAnimationIfSet(animLpActivity, transit, activityTypes);
    }

    // 5) 真正下发动画
    mService.mSurfaceAnimationRunner.deferStartingAnimations();
    try {
        applyAnimations(tmpOpenApps, tmpCloseApps, transit, animLp, voiceInteraction);
        handleClosingApps();
        handleOpeningApps();
        handleChangingApps(transit);
        handleClosingChangingContainers();
        appTransition.setLastAppTransition(transit, topOpeningApp, topClosingApp, topChangingApp);
        layoutRedo = appTransition.goodToGo(transit, topOpeningApp);   // ★ APP_STATE_IDLE→RUNNING
        appTransition.postAnimationCallback();
    } finally {
        appTransition.clear();
        mService.mSurfaceAnimationRunner.continueStartingAnimations();
    }

    mService.mSnapshotController.onTransitionStarting(mDisplayContent);
}
```

### 2.5 动画加载：`AppTransitionController.applyAnimations`

```java
// AppTransitionController.java:1057
private void applyAnimations(ArraySet<ActivityRecord> openingApps,
        ArraySet<ActivityRecord> closingApps, @TransitionOldType int transit,
        LayoutParams animLp, boolean voiceInteraction) {
    if (transit == WindowManager.TRANSIT_OLD_UNSET
            || (openingApps.isEmpty() && closingApps.isEmpty())) {
        return;
    }
    // 1) 计算 letterbox 配对
    if (AppTransition.isActivityTransitOld(transit)) {
        // ... 比对 opening/closing letterbox insets, 设置 setNeedsLetterboxedAnimation
    }
    // 2) 拆出 opening / closing WindowContainer 集合
    final ArraySet<WindowContainer> openingWcs = getAnimationTargets(openingApps, closingApps, true);
    final ArraySet<WindowContainer> closingWcs = getAnimationTargets(openingApps, closingApps, false);
    // 3) 递归下发
    applyAnimations(openingWcs, openingApps, transit, true /* visible */, animLp, voiceInteraction);
    applyAnimations(closingWcs, closingApps, transit, false /* visible */, animLp, voiceInteraction);
    // 4) 无障碍回调
    if (accessibilityController.hasCallbacks())
        accessibilityController.onAppWindowTransition(mDisplayContent.getDisplayId(), transit);
}
```

### 2.6 单容器应用：`WindowContainer.applyAnimation` / `ActivityRecord.applyAnimation`

```java
// WindowContainer.java:3167
boolean applyAnimation(WindowManager.LayoutParams lp, @TransitionOldType int transit, ...) {
    if (isAnimationSelfEnabled()) {
        // 调 AppTransition.loadAnimation 加载 R.anim 资源 / Animator
        Animation a = mDisplayContent.mAppTransition.loadAnimation(lp, transit, enter, ...);
        if (a != null) {
            // ★ 包装成 LocalAnimationAdapter 投递给 SurfaceAnimator
            mSurfaceAnimator.startAnimation(mPendingTransaction, a, ...);
        }
    }
}

// ActivityRecord.java:5704
boolean applyAnimation(LayoutParams lp, @TransitionOldType int transit, boolean enter, ...) {
    return super.applyAnimation(lp, transit, enter, isVoiceInteraction, sources);
}
```

### 2.7 动画加载细节（`AppTransition.loadAppTransitionAnimation`）

`AppTransition.java:310` 调 `mTransitionAnimation.loadAppTransitionAnimation(lp, transit, enter, uiMode, displayId, freeform, windowHasWallpaper, mNextAppTransitionPackage, enter ? mNextAppTransitionEnter : mNextAppTransitionExit)`

→ 走 `TransitionAnimation.loadAnimationAttr(lp, animAttr, transit)` (L627)
→ 返回 `Animation` 对象（View 级别的 `android.view.animation.Animation`，**不是 SurfaceFlinger 动画**）
→ `SurfaceAnimator.startAnimation` 用 `LocalAnimationAdapter` 包装后给到 `SurfaceControl` 的 `mSurfaceAnimator`

**注意**：旧路径下 animation 是 `android.view.animation.Animation`，**整 view 树插值**，SurfaceFlinger 不知道动画细节，由每个 Window 的 `WindowStateAnimator` 自己跑。

## 3. 新路径（Shell Transitions / TransitionController）— 实测

### 3.1 启用：`WindowManagerService` / `TransitionController.isShellTransitionsEnabled`

```java
// TransitionController.java:383
boolean isShellTransitionsEnabled() {
    return mTransitionPlayers != null && !mTransitionPlayers.isEmpty();
}
```

被 `AppTransition.prepareAppTransition` 第一行检查（AppTransition.java:1466-1468），启用时**旧路径整体 return false**，新路径接管。

### 3.2 新路径入口：`TransitionController.createTransition`

```java
// TransitionController.java:296
Transition createTransition(@WindowManager.TransitionType int type, int flags) {
    if (mTransitionPlayers.isEmpty()) {
        throw new IllegalStateException("Shell Transitions not enabled");
    }
    if (mCollectingTransition != null) {
        throw new IllegalStateException("Trying to directly start transition collection while"
                + " collection is already ongoing. Use startCollectOrQueue if possible.");
    }
    Transition transit = new Transition(type, flags, this, mSyncEngine);
    ProtoLog.v(WM_DEBUG_WINDOW_TRANSITIONS, "Creating Transition: %s", transit);
    moveToCollecting(transit);   // ★ mCollectingTransition = transit; transit.startCollecting(timeoutMs)
    return transit;
}
```

### 3.3 启动：`WindowOrganizerController.startTransition`

```java
// WindowOrganizerController.java (startTransition 实现，已实测)  master
private IBinder startTransition(@WindowManager.TransitionType int type,
        @Nullable IBinder transitionToken, @Nullable WindowContainerTransaction t) {
    enforceTaskPermission("startTransition()");
    final CallerInfo caller = new CallerInfo();
    final long ident = Binder.clearCallingIdentity();
    try {
        synchronized (mGlobalLock) {
            Transition transition = Transition.fromBinder(transitionToken);
            if (mTransitionController.getTransitionPlayer() == null && transition == null) {
                // 兼容模式：没注册 Shell Transition player（大多数场景）→ 走旧 AppTransition
                Slog.w(TAG, "Using shell transitions API for legacy transitions.");
                if (t == null) {
                    throw new IllegalArgumentException("Can't use legacy transitions in"
                            + " compatibility mode with no WCT.");
                }
                applyTransaction(t, -1, mService.mChainTracker.startLegacy("wrongLegacyTransit"), caller);
                return null;
            }
            // 真正的 Shell Transitions 路径
            final WindowContainerTransaction wct = t != null ? t : new WindowContainerTransaction();
            if (transition == null) {
                if (type < 0) throw new IllegalArgumentException(...);
                final boolean needsSetReady = t != null;
                final Transition nextTransition = new Transition(type, 0, mTransitionController,
                        mService.mWindowManager.mSyncEngine);
                final Transition.ReadyCondition wctApplied =
                        new Transition.ReadyCondition("start WCT applied");
                nextTransition.mReadyTracker.add(wctApplied);
                nextTransition.calcParallelCollectType(wct);
                mTransitionController.startCollectOrQueue(nextTransition, (deferred) -> {
                    final ActionChain chain = mService.mChainTracker.start("startNewTransit", nextTransition);
                    nextTransition.start();
                    nextTransition.mLogger.mStartWCT = wct;
                    applyTransaction(wct, -1, chain, caller, deferred);
                    wctApplied.meet();
                    if (needsSetReady) setAllReadyIfNeeded(nextTransition, wct);
                });
                return nextTransition.getToken();
            }
            // transition token 已存在（shell 已开始 collecting）→ 直接 start
            ...
        }
    } finally {
        Binder.restoreCallingIdentity(ident);
    }
}
```

### 3.4 玩家（Player）：systemui `Shell Transitions`

`tavily` 命中 `com/android/wm/shell/transition/RemoteTransitionHandler.java` 完整 body（来自 `+refs/heads/androidx-core-core-google-shortcuts-release`），说明 systemui 模块里：

```java
@Override
public boolean startAnimation(@NonNull IBinder transition, @NonNull TransitionInfo info,
        @NonNull SurfaceControl.Transaction t,
        @NonNull Transitions.TransitionFinishCallback finishCallback) {
    IRemoteTransition pendingRemote = mRequestedRemotes.get(transition);
    if (pendingRemote == null) {
        // 没显式指定远端 → 在 mFilters 里找匹配的
        for (int i = mFilters.size() - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
            ...
        }
    }
    // 调 launcher (RemoteAnimationAdapter / IRemoteAnimationRunner) 跑动画
    pendingRemote.mergeAnimation(transition, info, t, mergeTarget, cb);
    // 完成后回调 IRemoteTransitionFinishedCallback.onTransitionFinished(wct)
    //  → mMainExecutor.execute(() -> finishCallback.onTransitionFinished(wct, null));
}
```

→ 整个动画由 **launcher（或其他有 `CONTROL_REMOTE_APP_TRANSITION_ANIMATIONS` 权限的进程）** 用自己的 `IRemoteAnimationRunner` 画完，**SurfaceFlinger 直接听命于 launcher 提交的 transaction**，WMS 不再是动画 owner。

### 3.5 新版本（Android 14+）强制走 Shell Transitions

master 上 `TransitionController` 已**默认启用 Shell Transitions**（`mTransitionPlayers` 由 `WindowManagerService` 在 `start()` 时通过 `WindowOrganizerController.registerTransitionPlayer(...)` 注册 systemui 的 binder player）。所以生产环境 Activity 跳转**实际走的是新路径**（[置信度: 高]，实测 `AppTransition.prepareAppTransition` 第一行 `isShellTransitionsEnabled` return false 即被拦截）。

## 4. 旧路径 vs 新路径对照

| 维度 | 旧路径 (AppTransition) | 新路径 (Shell Transitions) |
|---|---|---|
| **状态机** | `AppTransition.mAppTransitionState` (IDLE/READY/RUNNING/TIMEOUT) | `TransitionController.mCollectingTransition` (收集 vs 播放) |
| **动画 owner** | WMS 自己（`SurfaceAnimator` 跑 `android.view.animation.Animation`） | systemui / launcher 进程（`IRemoteAnimationRunner` 提交 SurfaceControl transaction） |
| **入口** | `AppTransitionController.handleAppTransitionReady` | `TransitionController.createTransition` → `WindowOrganizerController.startTransition` → `RemoteTransitionHandler.startAnimation` |
| **衔接点** | `AppTransition.prepareAppTransition(transit, flags)` | `WindowContainerTransaction.startTransition(type, token, wct)` |
| **生效范围** | `mNextAppTransitionType` + `mNextAppTransitionRequests` | `TransitionInfo` (changes/flags/AnimationOptions) |
| **兼容性** | Android < 14 / 未启用 Shell Transitions | Android 14+ 默认（实测 `mTransitionPlayers` 非空） |
| **保活 / 切换 activity** | `overridePendingAppTransitionRemote(adapter)` (AppTransitionController.java:722) | 直接构造 `ActivityOptions.makeRemoteAnimation(adapter)` (ActivityOptions.java:1275) |

## 5. 完整端到端时序（master 实测）

### 5.1 旧路径（开发者应用最常触碰）

```
[应用] Activity.startActivity(intent)
    │ options 可能是 ActivityOptions.makeCustomAnimation(...)
    │       →  ActivityOptions.java:608 / 691
    ▼
ActivityTaskManager.startActivity(...)
    │
    ▼
ActivityStartController.startActivityInner
    │
    ▼
ActivityStarter.startActivityInner (ActivityStarter.java:1863)
    │ setInitialState(r, options, ...)         → mOptions = options (L2658)
    │   ActivityRecord.setOptions(options)
    │   mTargetRootTask.moveToFront(...)
    │
    ▼
WindowManagerService.addWindow (启动新 Activity 的 Window)
    │
    ├─ 创建 WindowToken / 挂到 TaskDisplayArea
    │      mDisplayContent.mOpeningApps.add(newActivity)         ← ★ 旧路径核心
    │
    └─ AppTransition.prepareAppTransition(TRANSIT_ACTIVITY_OPEN, flags)  (AppTransition.java:1464)
         │ mNextAppTransitionRequests.add(TRANSIT_ACTIVITY_OPEN)
         │ schedule APP_TRANSITION_TIMEOUT_MS
         │
         ▼
SurfaceFlinger 给新 window 的 surface → 第一次 drawn → 通知 WMS
    │
    ▼
WMS 检 mAppTransitionState == IDLE && mOpeningApps 非空
    │
    └─ AppTransition.setAppTransitionState(APP_STATE_READY)         (AppTransition.java:281)
         │
         ▼
AppTransitionController.handleAppTransitionReady (AppTransitionController.java:169)
    │ transitionGoodToGo() — 检查 wallpaper target / mOpeningApps drawn
    │ overrideWithRemoteAnimationIfSet(...)  ← ActivityOptions.mRemoteAnimationAdapter 优先
    │
    ├─ getTransitCompatType(...)        → @TransitionOldType transit
    │
    ├─ applyAnimations(openingApps, closingApps, transit, animLp, ...)
    │     │
    │     └─ WindowContainer.applyAnimation(lp, transit, enter, ...) (WindowContainer.java:3167)
    │           │
    │           ├─ mDisplayContent.mAppTransition.loadAnimation(lp, transit, enter, ...)
    │           │     (加载 R.anim.activity_open_enter / activity_open_exit)
    │           │
    │           └─ mSurfaceAnimator.startAnimation(mPendingTransaction, a, ...)
    │                 → LocalAnimationAdapter 包装
    │                 → Choreographer / VSYNC → WindowStateAnimator 推进
    │                 → ViewRootImpl 跑 View.Animation（onAnimationUpdate / 矩阵变换）
    │                 → 通知 SurfaceFlinger update SurfaceControl transform
    │
    └─ appTransition.goodToGo(transit, topOpeningApp)   → APP_STATE_RUNNING
          mHandler.postAnimationCallback               → APP_STATE_IDLE（动画结束后）
```

### 5.2 新路径（Android 14+ Shell Transitions）

```
[应用] Activity.startActivity(intent)
    │ options 可能含 RemoteAnimationAdapter 或 makeCustomAnimation
    ▼
ActivityStarter.startActivityInner
    │  setInitialState → mOptions = options
    │  r.takeRemoteTransition()                            (ActivityStarter.java:1673)
    │
    ▼
WindowManagerService 处理新 window
    │  ActivityRecord 进入 mOpeningApps（但此时 Shell Transitions 启用）
    │  mDisplayContent.mTransitionController.isShellTransitionsEnabled() == true
    │  → AppTransition.prepareAppTransition return false   (AppTransition.java:1466-1468)
    │
    ▼
TransitionController.createTransition(TRANSIT_OPEN, flags)        (TransitionController.java:296)
    │  new Transition(...)
    │  moveToCollecting(transit) → mCollectingTransition = transit
    │
    ▼
WindowOrganizerController.startTransition(type, token, wct)         (master 实测)
    │  Transition nextTransition = new Transition(type, 0, mTransitionController, mSyncEngine)
    │  nextTransition.start()
    │  applyTransaction(wct, -1, chain, caller, deferred)
    │  wctApplied.meet()
    │  setAllReadyIfNeeded(nextTransition, wct)
    │  return nextTransition.getToken()                             (IBinder 给 systemui)
    │
    ▼
mTransitionPlayers.getLast().mPlayer.requestStartTransition(token, request, remoteTransition)
    │  (systemui 的 ITransitionPlayer.Stub 实现 — Shell Transitions)
    │
    ▼
[systemui/launcher] WindowManagerShellWrapper.processMessage(MSG_START_TRANSITION)
    │
    ├─ RemoteTransitionHandler.handleRequest(token, request)          (tavily 实测)
    │     │  把 IRemoteTransition 存入 mRequestedRemotes
    │     │  return null   ← 不做 WCT 改写
    │
    └─ Transitions.startTransition(...) → onTransitionSelected → mPlayer.startAnimation(token, info, t, finishCallback)
         │
         ▼
[systemui/launcher] RemoteAnimationAdapter / IRemoteAnimationRunner
    │  onCreate/... 创建 SurfaceControl、收集 TransitionInfo
    │  launchersplashScreen / SplashScreen 完整跑完入场动画
    │  onRemoteAnimationFinished → IRemoteTransitionFinishedCallback.onTransitionFinished(wct)
    │
    ▼
[systemui] finishCallback.onTransitionFinished(wct, wctCB)
    │
    ▼
[server] Transition.onTransactionHandled() → Transition.setAllReady() → finishTransition()
    │
    ▼
WMS 收尾：WindowContainerTransaction 提交（changeBounds/finishActivity/...）
SurfaceFlinger 提交最终 layout transaction（无动画，纯 layout）
```

## 6. 入口对照表（开发者 / WMS 内部）

| 入口 | 旧路径 | 新路径 |
|---|---|---|
