# Activity 跳转动画衔接 + WMS 代码流程完整梳理

[知识来源: AOSP master 实测 - AppTransition / AppTransitionController / Transition / TransitionController / WindowOrganizerController / ActivityOptions / ActivityStarter / ActivityStartController / TaskFragment / DisplayContent 2026-07-18]
