            Transition transition = Transition.fromBinder(transitionToken);
            if (mTransitionController.getTransitionPlayer() == null && transition == null) {
                // 兼容模式：没注册 Shell Transition player（大多数场景）→ 走旧 AppTransition
                Slog.w(TAG, "Using shell transitions API for legacy transitions.");
                if (t == null) {
                    throw new IllegalArgumentException("Can't use legacy transitions in"
                            + " compatibility mode with no WCT.");
                }
                applyTransaction(t, -1, mService.mChainTracker.startLegacy("wrongLegacyTransit"), caller);
                return null;
            }
            // 真正的 Shell Transitions 路径
            final WindowContainerTransaction wct = t != null ? t : new WindowContainerTransaction();
            if (transition == null) {
                if (type < 0) throw new IllegalArgumentException(...);
                final boolean needsSetReady = t != null;
                final Transition nextTransition = new Transition(type, 0, mTransitionController,
                        mService.mWindowManager.mSyncEngine);
                final Transition.ReadyCondition wctApplied =
                        new Transition.ReadyCondition("start WCT applied");
                nextTransition.mReadyTracker.add(wctApplied);
                nextTransition.calcParallelCollectType(wct);
                mTransitionController.startCollectOrQueue(nextTransition, (deferred) -> {
                    final ActionChain chain = mService.mChainTracker.start("startNewTransit", nextTransition);
                    nextTransition.start();
                    nextTransition.mLogger.mStartWCT = wct;
                    applyTransaction(wct, -1, chain, caller, deferred);
                    wctApplied.meet();
                    if (needsSetReady) setAllReadyIfNeeded(nextTransition, wct);
                });
                return nextTransition.getToken();
            }
            // transition token 已存在（shell 已开始 collecting）→ 直接 start
            ...
        }
    } finally {
        Binder.restoreCallingIdentity(ident);
    }
}
```

### 3.4 玩家（Player）：systemui `Shell Transitions`

`tavily` 命中 `com/android/wm/shell/transition/RemoteTransitionHandler.java` 完整 body（来自 `+refs/heads/androidx-core-core-google-shortcuts-release`），说明 systemui 模块里：

```java
@Override
public boolean startAnimation(@NonNull IBinder transition, @NonNull TransitionInfo info,
        @NonNull SurfaceControl.Transaction t,
        @NonNull Transitions.TransitionFinishCallback finishCallback) {
    IRemoteTransition pendingRemote = mRequestedRemotes.get(transition);
    if (pendingRemote == null) {
        // 没显式指定远端 → 在 mFilters 里找匹配的
        for (int i = mFilters.size() - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
            ...
        }
    }
    // 调 launcher (RemoteAnimationAdapter / IRemoteAnimationRunner) 跑动画
    pendingRemote.mergeAnimation(transition, info, t, mergeTarget, cb);
    // 完成后回调 IRemoteTransitionFinishedCallback.onTransitionFinished(wct)
    //  → mMainExecutor.execute(() -> finishCallback.onTransitionFinished(wct, null));
}
```

→ 整个动画由 **launcher（或其他有 `CONTROL_REMOTE_APP_TRANSITION_ANIMATIONS` 权限的进程）** 用自己的 `IRemoteAnimationRunner` 画完，**SurfaceFlinger 直接听命于 launcher 提交的 transaction**，WMS 不再是动画 owner。

### 3.5 新版本（Android 14+）强制走 Shell Transitions

master 上 `TransitionController` 已**默认启用 Shell Transitions**（`mTransitionPlayers` 由 `WindowManagerService` 在 `start()` 时通过 `WindowOrganizerController.registerTransitionPlayer(...)` 注册 systemui 的 binder player）。所以生产环境 Activity 跳转**实际走的是新路径**（[置信度: 高]，实测 `AppTransition.prepareAppTransition` 第一行 `isShellTransitionsEnabled` return false 即被拦截）。

## 4. 旧路径 vs 新路径对照

| 维度 | 旧路径 (AppTransition) | 新路径 (Shell Transitions) |
|---|---|---|
| **状态机** | `AppTransition.mAppTransitionState` (IDLE/READY/RUNNING/TIMEOUT) | `TransitionController.mCollectingTransition` (收集 vs 播放) |
| **动画 owner** | WMS 自己（`SurfaceAnimator` 跑 `android.view.animation.Animation`） | systemui / launcher 进程（`IRemoteAnimationRunner` 提交 SurfaceControl transaction） |
| **入口** | `AppTransitionController.handleAppTransitionReady` | `TransitionController.createTransition` → `WindowOrganizerController.startTransition` → `RemoteTransitionHandler.startAnimation` |
| **衔接点** | `AppTransition.prepareAppTransition(transit, flags)` | `WindowContainerTransaction.startTransition(type, token, wct)` |
| **生效范围** | `mNextAppTransitionType` + `mNextAppTransitionRequests` | `TransitionInfo` (changes/flags/AnimationOptions) |
| **兼容性** | Android < 14 / 未启用 Shell Transitions | Android 14+ 默认（实测 `mTransitionPlayers` 非空） |
| **保活 / 切换 activity** | `overridePendingAppTransitionRemote(adapter)` (AppTransitionController.java:722) | 直接构造 `ActivityOptions.makeRemoteAnimation(adapter)` (ActivityOptions.java:1275) |

